<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4808317>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Larva of Serratella palatovi Martynov, Selvakumar & Jacobus, sp. nov., regular (non-type) specimen (A) and holotype (B–F). A.—total view of larva; B.—head; C, D.—stout setae of occipital protuberances; E.—thorax, dorsal view; F.—thorax, lateral view. Scale bar 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4808317/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4808321>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Larva of Serratella palatovi Martynov, Selvakumar & Jacobus, sp. nov., holotype (A, B, E–G) and regular (nontype) specimen (C, D). A, B.—mandibles; C.—labrum; D.—hypopharynx; E.—maxillary palp; F.—apical half of maxilla; G.—labium." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4808321/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4808327>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Larva of Serratella palatovi Martynov, Selvakumar & Jacobus, sp. nov., holotype. A.—fore femur; B.—middle femur; C.—hind femur; D.—stout setae of dorsal surface and outer margin of fore femur; E–H.—stout setae of dorsal surface of middle femur; I, J.—tarsal claws." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4808327/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4808333>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Larva of Serratella palatovi Martynov, Selvakumar & Jacobus, sp. nov., holotype. A.—abdomen, lateral view; B.—posterolateral projections of terga VIII and IX; C.—abdomen, dorsal view; D–G.—gills IV–VII; H.—caudal filaments." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4808333/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4808393>
    dc:description "FIGURE 20. Habitats of Torleya simbalbarensis Selvakumar, Subramanian, Martynov & Jacobus, sp. nov. (A), Serratella palatovi Martynov, Selvakumar & Jacobus, sp. nov. (B, C) and Torleya dibruensis Selvakumar, Martynov & Jacobus, sp. nov. (D). A.—stream in Simbalbara Wildlife Sanctuary, Sirmour District, Himachal Pradesh, India; B.—stream-main source of the Klang Phat River, Chom Thong District, Chiang Mai Province, Thailand; C.—stream in Tale Valley, Lower Subansiri District, Arunachal Pradesh, India; D.—Dibru River, Papum Pare District, Arunachal Pradesh, India." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4808393/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

